entries.fs_response01: Oh... I feel like I'm going to...
entries.fs_response02: My stomach. It feels like it's going to burst!
entries.fs_response03: Why are we so sick? They are doing something to us to make us this way!
entries.fs_response05: The bacta they are using has been contaminated with something. We've all been infected.
entries.fs_response06: Better... Better get a bucket I'm going to throw up.
entries.fs_response07: I just hope they clean some of this up, soon.
